{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures-v8/learn-introductory-javascript-by-building-a-pyramid-generator/step-6","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-introductory-javascript-by-building-a-pyramid-generator","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 6","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada deklarišete parametar za glavnu reč <code>let</code>, možete <dfn>ponovo postaviti vrednost</dfn> (ili promeniti vrednost) tog parametra kasnije. U ovom primeru, vrednost <code>programmer</code> se menja iz <code>\"Naomi\"</code> u <code>\"CamperChan\"</code>.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let programmer = \"Naomi\";\nprogrammer = \"CamperChan\";\n</code></pre>\n<p>Zapamtite da kada ponovo postavite vrednost parametru, ponovo ćete prikazati ključnu reč <code>let</code>.</p>\n<p>Nakon vašeg <code>console.log</code>, postavite vrednost <code>\"World\"</code> za vaš parametar <code>character</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"660ef31a5be625914a0102cd","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures-v8","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures-v8/learn-introductory-javascript-by-building-a-pyramid-generator/step-6"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"let character = 'Hello';\nconsole.log(character);\n","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[0,4],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Moraš koristiti <code>character</code> dva puta u svoj kod.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/character/g), 3);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristiš operater dodeljivanja za ponovno postavljanje vrednosti za <code>character</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/character\\s*\\=/g), 2);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristiš niz znakova <code>\"World\"</code> u svom kodu.</p>","testString":"assert.match(__helpers.removeJSComments(code), /(\"|')World\\1/);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš parametar za <code>character</code> mora imati vrednost <code>\"World\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(character, \"World\");"},{"text":"<p>Postavljanje vrednosti više ne bi trebalo da koristi <code>let</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isBelow(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/let/g).length, 2);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures-v8/#learn-introductory-javascript-by-building-a-pyramid-generator","dashedName":"step-6","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures-v8","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures-v8","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-introductory-javascript-by-building-a-pyramid-generator","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures-v8/learn-introductory-javascript-by-building-a-pyramid-generator/step-7","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures-v8/learn-introductory-javascript-by-building-a-pyramid-generator/step-5","id":"660ef31a5be625914a0102cd","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"const character = \"!\";\nconst count = 10;\nconst rows = [];\nlet inverted = false;\n\nfunction padRow(rowNumber, rowCount) {\n  return \" \".repeat(rowCount - rowNumber) + character.repeat(2 * rowNumber - 1) + \" \".repeat(rowCount - rowNumber);\n}\n\nfor (let i = 1; i <= count; i++) {\n  if (inverted) {\n    rows.unshift(padRow(i, count));\n  } else {\n    rows.push(padRow(i, count));\n  }\n}\n\nlet result = \"\"\n\nfor (const row of rows) {\n  result = result + row + \"\\n\";\n}\n\nconsole.log(result);","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures-v8/learn-introductory-javascript-by-building-a-pyramid-generator/step-6"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}